{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-post-js","path":"/post/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"춤추는 기술 블로그","comment":{"utterances":"ensia96/ensia96.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"ensia96"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8045abfe-05ee-5be9-844a-c287c0c29c24","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A0%84%EC%A0%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4\">전제 조건</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%95%9C-%EC%A4%84-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\">한 줄 요약</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">방법</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"전제 조건 항목 내용 버전 프로그래밍 언어 Python 3.7.4 한 줄 요약  대신 (+ 추가 메서드) 을 활용한다. 방법 시스템 모듈을 가져온 뒤, 외부의 입력을 받을 부분에 코드를 추가한다. 입력의 특징에 따라, 아래와 같이 코드를 추가한다. (예시 주석 참고) 20220214 - 표기 수정(메소드 -> 메서드)","html":"<h2 id=\"전제-조건\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%84%EC%A0%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4\" aria-label=\"전제 조건 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>전제 조건</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>항목</th>\n<th>내용</th>\n<th>버전</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>프로그래밍 언어</td>\n<td>Python</td>\n<td>3.7.4</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">환경이 다른 경우, 글의 내용이 도움이 되지 않을 수 있음</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"한-줄-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%9C-%EC%A4%84-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"한 줄 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>한 줄 요약</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">input()</code> 대신 <code class=\"language-text\">sys.stdin.readline()</code>(+ 추가 메서드) 을 활용한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>방법</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>시스템 모듈을 가져온 뒤, 외부의 입력을 받을 부분에 코드를 추가한다.\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> sys\n\ncode_for_input <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> sys<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>stdin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>readline<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>입력의 특징에 따라, 아래와 같이 코드를 추가한다. (예시 주석 참고)\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\">sys<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>stdin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>readline<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># a => \"a\\n\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># a b c d => \"a b c d\\n\"</span>\n\nsys<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>stdin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>readline<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>strip<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># a => \"a\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># a b c d => \"a b c d\"</span>\n\nsys<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>stdin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>readline<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>split<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># a => [\"a\"]</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># a b c d => [\"a\", \"b\", \"c\", \"d\"]</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li>20220214 - 표기 수정(메소드 -> 메서드)</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"파이썬에서 많은 입력을 빠르게 받는 법","tags":["Tip","Python"],"date":"August 25, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","4018478212"]}